videos.description: Kyle Washington absolutely owns the paint, securing multiple offensive rebounds before finally getting one to drop for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Washington dominates the boards

videos.description: Gary Clark climbs the ladder to swat a shot attempt into the Bearcats' bench in the first half.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Clark denies UConn

videos.description: Jalen Adams blows by his defender on his way to the basket for an easy two for the Huskies.
videos.headline: UConn's Adams attacks the rack

videos.description: Keith Williams sinks a 3-pointer as time expires in the first half, deflating UConn's home crowd.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Williams nails 3-pointer at buzzer

videos.description: Kyle Washington gets the dish from Gary Clark and stuffs in the two-handed slam in the second half.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Washington throws it down
